<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>TheCricAuction - Home</title>
  <style>
    /* Global styles */
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(to top, #f58754, #1a237e);
      background-color: #1a237e;
      background-size: cover; /* Ensures the background covers the entire viewport */
      background-attachment: fixed;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      /* text-align: center; */
    }
    .header-section {
	  text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .header-section h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .info-section {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
	.info-section h2, p{
		text-align: center;
	}
    .info-section h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .info-section p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .home {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .inner-home {
      flex: 1 0 200px; /* Adjust width as needed */
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .inner-home a {
      display: block;
      padding: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      background-color: #f57224;
      color: #fff;
      border: 5px solid #f58754;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .inner-home a:hover {
      background-color: #f58754;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container header-section">
    <h1>Welcome to iLead Cricket League</h1>
    <p>Explore the following options to streamline your league management:</p>
  </div>

  <div class="home">
    <div class="inner-home">
      <a href="<%= admin_users_path %>" target="_blank">Manage Players</a>
    </div>
    <div class="inner-home">
      <a href="<%= teams_data_path %>" target="_blank">Teams Insights</a>
    </div>
    <div class="inner-home">
      <a href="<%= teams_path %>" target="_blank">Manage Teams</a>
    </div>
    <div class="inner-home">
      <a href="<%= users_path %>" target="_blank">Go to Auction </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container info-section">
	<h2>About TheCricAuction</h2>
	<p>TheCricAuction is a specialized platform designed for cricket leagues, offering:</p>
	<!-- <ul style="list-style-type: none;"> -->
	<ul>
	  <li>Efficient player auction and team data management.</li>
	  <li>Place bids, set bid limits, and monitor bidding activity.</li>
	  <li>Create, modify, and manage team and player profiles.</li>
	  <li>Allocate budgets and manage team finances.</li>
	  <li>Email notifications for auction events and player details.</li>
	  <li>Customize auction rules, settings, and formats.</li>
	  <li>Customizable features to adapt to different league requirements.</li>
	</ul>
	<p>Empower your cricket league with TheCricAuction's tailored features and elevate your management experience today.</p>
  </div>
  
</body>
</html>
